{"word":"διαπνέω","slug":"διαπνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαπνέω</b></el> <el>(epic <el>-πνείω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πνεύσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to blow through</i>: — <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>αὔραις διαπνεῖσθαι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to breathe between times, get breath</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to disperse in vapour</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}